title: Zombie Survival Shooter
content: Zombie Survival Shooter is an intense action game where you fight against waves of zombies. Use WASD keys to move your character and mouse to aim and shoot. Survive as long as possible by eliminating zombies and collecting power-ups. The game features multiple weapons including pistols, shotguns, and rifles. Strategy tips: Keep moving to avoid being surrounded, aim for headshots for maximum damage, and collect ammo boxes regularly. Upgrade your weapons between waves to increase your survival chances. Perfect for fans of zombie apocalypse and survival horror games!

title: Subway Surfers
content: Subway Surfers is an endless runner game where you surf the subways and dodge trains. Use arrow keys to move left/right, jump, and roll. Collect coins and power-ups to boost your score. Tips: Time your jumps carefully, grab the jetpack for easy coins, and watch out for barriers!

title: 2048 Puzzle
content: 2048 is a sliding block puzzle game. Use arrow keys to slide tiles in four directions. When two tiles with the same number touch, they merge into one. Your goal is to create a tile with the number 2048. Strategy tip: Keep your highest tile in one corner and build around it!
